mal=\"https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/laptopmag/media/img/missing-image.svg\" data-srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/Y9DiNzmAjwaXYUKAYuJthF-320-80.jpg 320w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/Y9DiNzmAjwaXYUKAYuJthF-650-80.jpg 650w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/Y9DiNzmAjwaXYUKAYuJthF-970-80.jpg 970w\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/Y9DiNzmAjwaXYUKAYuJthF.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/Y9DiNzmAjwaXYUKAYuJthF.jpg\" data-ll-status=\"loaded\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; top: 0px; left: 0px; position: absolute; height: 338.625px; width: 602px; background-color: unset; object-fit: contain;\"></picture></p></div></div><figcaption itemprop=\"caption description\" class=\" inline-layout\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 16px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; display: inline-block; width: 602px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span class=\"credit\" itemprop=\"copyrightHolder\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 16px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 12px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-break: break-word; display: inline-block;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">(Crédito da imagem: Square Enix)</font></font></span></figcaption></figure></div><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\" align=\"center\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Schyman compôs para a série Bioshock, Guild Wars 2, ambos os jogos Middle Earth: Shadow e muito mais.<span>&nbsp;</span></font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Considerando o quão intensa, atmosférica e emocional a trilha sonora de Bioshock pode ser, estou animado para ver como sua música pode melhorar Forspoken.&nbsp;</font></font></p><h2 id=\"forspoken-ray-tracing\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.7em; padding: 10px 0px 0px; border: 0px none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 30px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; vertical-align: baseline; width: 602px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); clear: both; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\" align=\"center\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Traçado de raio Forspoken</font></font></h2><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\" align=\"center\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">O Forspoken contará com a tecnologia de rastreamento de raios, conforme confirmado pelo presidente da Square Enix, Yosuke Matsuda.<span>&nbsp;</span></font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Conforme traduzido pela<span>&nbsp;</span></font></font><a href=\"https://www.gematsu.com/2020/07/project-athia-is-an-open-world-game-according-to-square-enix-president\" data-url=\"https://www.gematsu.com/2020/07/project-athia-is-an-open-world-game-according-to-square-enix-president\" data-component-tracked=\"1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(94, 105, 228); text-decoration: none;\"><u style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Gematsu</font></font></u></a><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span>&nbsp;</span>, Matusda afirma que “o PS5 melhora drasticamente a tecnologia de vídeo, como com a implementação da tecnologia de \'rastreamento de raios\' refletora de luz.<span>&nbsp;</span></font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Comparado com o que você vê no PC, é quase idêntico.<span>&nbsp;</span></font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Ao utilizar essas características especiais, somos capazes de criar imagens incrivelmente precisas. ”</font></font></p><div align=\"center\"><figure class=\" inline-layout\" data-bordeaux-image-check=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><div class=\"image-full-width-wrapper\" style=\"margin: 0px auto 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; width: 602px;\"><div class=\"image-widthsetter\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; width: 602px; max-width: 1920px;\"><p class=\"vanilla-image-block\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 338.625px 0px 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 0; font-family: inherit; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; position: relative; height: 0px;\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" alt=\"Forspoken\" class=\" lazy-image-van optional-image\" data-normal=\"https://vanilla.futurecdn.net